{"tid":628821,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求問關於大專生notebook ownership program詳情同notebook選擇!","createTime":"2018-04-14T08:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T08:17:12.000Z","uid":182030,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6887c3cd968c56e78cdeeec7c118de673a0868d8","tid":628821,"uid":182030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:06:14.000Z","msg":"話說打算今個暑期買notebook<br />\n<br />\n咁Lenovo嘅學生優惠有兩隻: 1. educational store 2. 大專生ownership program<br />\n咁就聽聞大專生ownership program會平d，又有贈品嗰d<br />\n<br />\n咁我想買Lenovo ThinkPad t480s， 配置上我都想改好多嘢，升ram, ssd,換mon等<br />\n<br />\n問題來了，想問個ownership program d 電腦offer，配置上係咪fix死咗? 可否改配置或有其他配置組合揀?<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係個educational store到7月又會唔會再平d?<br />\n<br />\n有冇任何經驗者，求解答，一萬個thanks! 主要考慮緊而家買，定等7,8月<br />\n<br />\nby the way聽聞 windows對2k mon支援較差，有冇咩例子?因為睇評測，個個都話t480s個mon真的比較差，色域45%，偏暗and黃<br />\n<br />\n關於notebook選擇方面，若果同Dell xps15 9570 (五月出) 最低配比，大家會點揀?<br />\n聽聞Dell xps15 2018 五月出，都係8代cpu，低配就應該如圖，應該同9560一樣<br />\n對呢部做嘅research不及thinkpad多，因為自己主觀上比較like thinkpad系列，但見好多人都推薦xps 15 9560，想知道佢嘅擴充性同缺點<br />\n<br />\n咁參考上年ownership program xps15 9560低配就$11998 (2018版應該頂多貴1000掛)，而家我自己customize嘅 t480s就$11645，價錢差不多。<br />\n都係同一個問題，有冇人上年ownership program買xps15? 有冇其他配置揀?<br />\n<br />\n利申: <br />\n想襟用，捱到五年以上<br />\n下年year 4，畢業後應該不會成日拎出街，所以便攜因素未去到好重大<br />\n少打機，文書處理，得閒剪下片，會成日睇電影<br />\n<br />\n感謝大家幫忙!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/155623_4f69ef3fb91708c6e7a4987c95105adc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F155623_4f69ef3fb91708c6e7a4987c95105adc.jpg&h=e1400349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/155641_2c4fabc9bf567e82154e3dc662f88e44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F155641_2c4fabc9bf567e82154e3dc662f88e44.jpg&h=4bf7d0de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fdc